          "id": "hook",
          "label": "Hook",
          "startSec": 0,
          "endSec": 21.85,
          "text": "What if your project tracker was just files in your repository? No SaaS login. No per-seat costs. No external database to maintain. Kanbus is a lightweight issue tracker that lives entirely in your Git repo. Issues, plans, and execution stay connected in one place—right next to your code.",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "pause",
              "startSec": 0,
