          "id": "one_file",
          "label": "One File Per Issue",
          "startSec": 27.5,
          "endSec": 52.55,
          "text": "Every issue is a single JSON file. Not one giant file that causes merge conflicts every time two people touch it—one file per issue. That means your team and your AI agents can create, update, and close issues in parallel without stepping on each other. Hash-based IDs make collisions impossible, even when multiple agents are creating tasks at the same time.",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "tts",
              "startSec": 27.5,
              "endSec": 37.4,
              "text": "Every issue is a single JSON file. Not one giant file that causes merge conflicts every time two people touch it—one file per issue."
            },
            {
              "type": "pause",
              "startSec": 37.4,
              "endSec": 37.699999999999996,
              "durationSec": 0.3
            },
            {
              "type": "tts",
              "startSec": 37.699999999999996,
              "endSec": 52.55,
              "text": "That means your team and your AI agents can create, update, and close issues in parallel without stepping on each other. Hash-based IDs make collisions impossible, even when multiple agents are creating tasks at the same time."
            }
          ],
          "bullets": []
        },
        {
          "id": "no_friction",
          "label": "No Friction",
          "startSec": 52.55,
          "endSec": 63.55,
          "text": "There's no database server to maintain, no background process to crash, and no complex synchronization logic. Each command just scans the project files directly.",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "pause",
              "startSec": 52.55,
              "endSec": 52.849999999999994,
